Wrapping up data in single unit which is class.
Encapsulation is all about hiding data members/variables.


Abstraction vs Encapsulation
  Abstraction hides method implementation
  Encapsulation hides data members


With the help of getter and setter method we can use encapsulation

if we have multiple private variables and we have to access all then we can go with the constructor
and if we have to access specific variables then we can go with te setter.
